<codeline><highlight class="normal">vcpkg<sp/>install<sp/>allegro5<sp/>--triplet=x86-windows<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>;<sp/>for<sp/>win32</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">vcpkg<sp/>install<sp/>allegro5<sp/>--triplet=x64-windows<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>;<sp/>for<sp/>win64</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">vcpkg<sp/>integrate<sp/>install<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>;<sp/>register<sp/>include<sp/>/<sp/>libs<sp/>in<sp/>Visual<sp/>Studio</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
